# Specs Folder

The specs directory defines system behavior before code generation.

Folders

features
state
ui-tree
component-graph
dependency-graph
task-graph

Each feature must define

feature.spec.md
feature.state.md
feature.ui-tree.md
feature.graph.md
feature.dependencies.md
feature.tasks.md

Specs must describe

user flow
state transitions
UI structure
dependencies
implementation tasks
